---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const siteUrl = 'https://unitcalc.io';
---
<BaseLayout title="Cookie Policy | UnitCalc" description="Cookie Policy for UnitCalc. We use minimal, privacy-respecting cookies.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 prose-content">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-navy-900 mb-2">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-8">Last updated: January 2025</p>
    <h2>What Are Cookies?</h2>
    <p>Cookies are small data files stored in your browser. UnitCalc uses <code>localStorage</code> (similar to cookies) to remember your preferences.</p>
    <h2>Cookies We Use</h2>
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>Name</th><th>Type</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Duration</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>unitcalc_cookie_consent</td><td>Essential</td><td>Stores your cookie consent choice</td><td>Until cleared</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <h2>Analytics Cookies (Optional)</h2>
    <p>If you choose "Accept All", we may use Google Analytics to understand anonymous usage patterns. These cookies do not identify you personally and can be refused by selecting "Necessary Only" on the cookie banner.</p>
    <h2>Managing Cookies</h2>
    <p>You can clear your browser's localStorage at any time via your browser settings. You can also change your consent preference by clearing site data for unitcalc.io.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:franruizlozano31@gmail.com" class="text-brand-600 hover:underline">franruizlozano31@gmail.com</a></p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
